The paper deals with a formalization of a logic for a polymorphic dual-intuitionistic/linear type theory with fixed points, and the construction of various types including recursive types. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Type Theory (cs.TL), Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL), and Computation and Language (cs.CL).
